2002-02-09

	Version 1.1.0 (devel) released. With this new release comes the
	added ability to control a process that is already running. 
	Tagged as devel, this build has not been extensively tested and 
	could have bugs.

2002-02-06

    Version 1.0.1 (stable) released. This updated is primarily because of
    updated build tools. Sloth now uses GNU Autotools for a standardized
    build process.

2002-02-02

	Version 1.0.0 (stable) released. First release of sloth, hooray! 
	
